{"about_the_game":"You thought it would be fun to break into a nearby museum and root through the artifacts stored there.  Little did you know that a dusty chest in the basement imprisoned the evil <i><strong>CHOP GOBLINS</strong></i>.  <br><br>Now they're loose, wrecking bladed havok on the world once again.  It's up to you to chase them through the city and across space and time, in a bespoke FPS campaign spanning the modern day, 1800's Transylvania, ancient Greece, and the not too distant future.<br><br><u><strong>And you can finish it in about 30 minutes!</strong></u><br><br>Chop Goblins is a &quot;microshooter&quot;:  An FPS designed to be completed in a single sitting, without sacrificing depth, variety, or creativity in its gameplay and level design.  It's a game you can play for less than an hour, or replay for many hours.  Need something to distract you from work, boredom, or grinding in other games?  Take a Chop Goblins Break, with a fun and satisfying FPS campaign that only takes one sitting to fully experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A short but densely packed campaign, designed to be all killer and no filler<br></li><li> 5 levels set in different time periods<br></li><li> 5 satisfying and unique weapons, from an antique flintlock to the Mk. II Impaler &quot;Vlad&quot; automatic stake gun<br></li><li> An assortment of different enemies and minibosses<br></li><li> Leaderboards, achievements, and secrets, for those seeking replayability</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shameless Promotion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1935660/5d78be76060fa8c27a58d9e4c1d5da9585c9469c.jpg"},{"name":"Ancient Relic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1935660/ea2b79a25bcc83fa8bc9ce772569bc7f6be1a2e4.jpg"},{"name":"Ionian and Doric Just Don't Cut It","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1935660/ed31